cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a method for human action recognition using Convolutional Neural Networks (ConvNets) applied to sequence-based data. This falls under the computer vision domain, which is typically categorized under cs.CV. The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which can be categorized under cs.LG and cs.AI. Additionally, the paper deals with multimodal data, which can be categorized under cs.MM. Finally, the paper involves score fusion techniques, which can be categorized under cs.NE.
